# Vendored, minified third-party assets. `-diff` collapses them to a single
# "Binary files differ" line so tools that inline `git diff` (e.g. Sandcastle's
# reviewer prompt) don't blow their context on 12k lines of minified code.
# `linguist-generated` also hides them in GitHub PR diffs.
skills/visual-teach/assets/katex/**   -diff linguist-generated
skills/visual-teach/assets/prism/**   -diff linguist-generated
*.min.js          -diff
*.min.css         -diff
